udy was produced based on nrPDB-2015 using SARST structure alignments and the BLOSUM algorithm [<xref rid="pone.0255076.ref077" ref-type="bibr">77</xref>]. See <xref rid="pone.0255076.s005" ref-type="supplementary-material">S4 File</xref> for the matrix and the details of its production.</p></list-item></list></p>
